{"comments":"MediaQuery — Type-safe CSS media query representation.\n\n**WHY MEDIAQUERY?**\nMedia queries in CSS are stringly typed and error-prone. This module\nprovides a type-safe ADT for media queries, eliminating JavaScript FFI\nfor media query matching and construction.\n\n**Supported Features:**\n- Width constraints (min-width, max-width)\n- Height constraints (min-height, max-height)\n- Orientation (portrait, landscape)\n- User preferences (color scheme, reduced motion)\n- Display characteristics (resolution, color depth)\n- Pointer capabilities (coarse, fine, none)\n- Combinators (and, or, not)\n\n**Use Cases:**\n- Responsive design breakpoints\n- Dark mode detection\n- Accessibility preferences\n- Device capability detection\n- Print styling\n\n## Dependencies\n- Prelude\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Dimension.Device (Pixel, PixelsPerInch)\n\n## Dependents\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Dimension.Breakpoint\n- Component.ThemeProvider\n- Hook.UseMediaQuery\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Device","Types"],"Pixel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[244,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/MediaQuery.purs","start":[244,3]},"title":"MinWidth"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Device","Types"],"Pixel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[246,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/MediaQuery.purs","start":[246,3]},"title":"MaxWidth"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Device","Types"],"Pixel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[248,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/MediaQuery.purs","start":[248,3]},"title":"MinHeight"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[